        ],
        [
          "You have been a dutiful Revenant to Justicar di Zagreb for decades.  You have served him faithfully.  You would always get him whatever he needs, and be ready for anything he might ask of you.  But\nyou never left his side when he had to travel abroad.  You've never felt comfortable around anyone outside of the Chantries of Clan Tremere, though.  A few months ago, after nearly 50 years of dutiful \nservice, di Zagreb rewarded you with the embrace of one of his childer.  You feel honored about this, but now you know the responsibilities are greater, knowing any misstep can cause harm to you and to\nyour Masters.  Maybe keeping your head down and doing your job is rewarding, but it's time to try out those new opportunities given to you.  You may not be best suited for social situations, but Tremere\ncannot succeed if they don't try."
        ],
